                            <comment id="14436402" author="bentmann" created="Sun, 6 Jun 2010 15:09:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?view=revision&amp;amp;revision=951948&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r951948&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A workaround for your case is to specify &lt;tt&gt;-Dclassifier=javadoc&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;-Dpackaging=jar&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14436384" author="tmoreira2020" created="Sun, 6 Jun 2010 21:54:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Benjamin! The workaround worked fine.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
